attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KJYT-je8i-JWbZ4Ou8P_display_text
attribs.current: If the elephant moves at least 20 feet straight toward a reature right before hitting it with a gore attack, the target must succeed on a DC 12 Strength save or be knocked prone. If the target is prone, the elephant can make one stomp attack against it as a bonus action.

attribs.current: When the elephant's rider makes an initiative roll all enemies within 90 feet that can see the elephant must save DC 12 wisdom or become frightened.of the elephant.
